42 "§ 105-129.82. (See notes) Sunset; studies.
43 (a) Sunset. – This Article is repealed effective for business activities that occur on or after
44 January 1, 2014.
45 (b) Equity Study. – The Department of Commerce shall study the effect of the tax
46 incentives provided in this Article on tax equity. This study shall include the following:
47 (1) Reexamining the formula in G.S. 143B-437.08 used to define development
48 tiers, to include consideration of alternative measures for more equitable
49 treatment of counties in similar economic circumstances.
50 (2) Considering whether the assignment of tiers and the applicable thresholds are
51 equitable for smaller counties.
